        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> sacrum <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Valius Festus conditor vineae huius <lb n="3"/>loci qui nunc Valianus a Festo dicitur <lb n="4"/>aeternumque tenet per saecula nomen <lb n="5"/>voto succepto <note>sic</note> aram adampliavit et <lb n="6"/>tauro immolando dedicavit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Position der Zeilenfälle in den Handschriften unterschiedlich überliefert. Z. 3 (ab QVI) u. 4: Hexameter in Anlehnung an Vergil, Aen. 4, 234. (B): CIL III 170*: Leseabweichungen.</p>
